<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> czu reden von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kauffleute notdurfft, als sy
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>wol</add> erczelen <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc., waz sy in
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache czu disem mal an ewr
                                <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> werb von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
